Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,束那麼高可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是分成三束比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我想轉換一下心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣不就幾乎是馬尾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺下的時候很礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指令已經先寫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給學生會的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快點回去比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請自便 有田春雪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾到你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫院真是太慎重了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論說了幾次 食物的味道都沒有改善
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好聽話 好好恢復身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是夕陽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的…夕陽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我聽錯了嗎 我記得昨天有問過你喜歡的髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 並不是沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在想 該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊 如果突然就說好話 似乎很客套 輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為不適合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是在勉強你說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 真的很適合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…所以…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉
Comment: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 去了倉嶋那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 和阿拓一起去 把所有的事情都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加速世界的事 阿拓設置了後門的事 一直騙她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 她說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常生氣 突然把辭典扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就含著眼淚 抱著我和阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果 那之後就沒理過我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 生氣也是當然的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事情上我也有一部分責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去向倉嶋道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是必須由我和阿拓來想辦法處理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好地贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贖罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得拓武是在新宿的中學上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他的腦袋比我和千百合還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就考去了國高中一貫制的學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動也萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 應該能成為「黑暗星雲」的強大戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(685,655)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也被他邀請一起去組隊對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是要在學姐出院前讓我升到等級2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜歡他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使被背叛 被傷害 也能互相原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能有這樣的朋友真令人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿拓是我的好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的決心沒有改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Comment: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小春也是阿拓也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有想說的事的話就來好好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真讓人不爽
Comment: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是完全飛行型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是感動的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 3 2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 三連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和完全飛行型戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能當成一個閒聊的話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,升級獎勵要好好考慮再選啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:08:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 學姐會替我高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 等級2還無法當成戰力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要著急 慢慢努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少到等級4為止我都會支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,義務？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在小春成為獨當一面的「超頻連線者」之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(826,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我也不認為那樣就能減少罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿拓要那麼想的話也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到底學姐受那麼嚴重的傷是因為我太遲鈍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我所造成的罪孽不是那麼簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到之前小千那樣 你也明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的罪孽有多深重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 今天就到這裡 「超頻登出」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(792,655)}<Burst Out>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 等等 那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 升級什麼的還…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 小春 快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保有「超頻點數」 8？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(643,655)}<Burst Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春 「超頻登出」！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(667,655)}<Burst Out>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 真的抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使到達了可升級的點數 也不能馬上升級
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這明明是一定要在事先就告訴你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個不合格的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是因為我太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有出現升級要消費300點的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是稍微想想就能明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我興奮得忘乎所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先確認一下現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的保有點數是8吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話 在同等級的對戰中被打敗的那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會「超頻點數」全損
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,655)}<Burst Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先通過直連對戰 將我的保有「點數」分一半給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(830,655)}<Point>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 選擇地點和時間 一點點來恢復點數
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過直連對戰來給我點數…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是說 阿拓要不抵抗地不斷輸給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他辦法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的點數上比較寬裕 這個方法應該是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種事不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然我單方面攻擊的阿拓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這種話的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點數歸零的話 你就會被強制卸載「Brain Burst」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠地失去這個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 你在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實 在直連對戰裡我突然襲擊過去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的點數打成0並不困難
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是討厭這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該說是玷污了戰鬥呢 又或者是不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐也為了保護我使用了「物理完全加速」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(864,655)}<Physical Full Burst>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點數應該也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 從來沒有要求我分給她點數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我要自願分給她的話 她肯定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然等級 力量 經驗都完全無法比較
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 作為「超頻連線者」一員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(686,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和學姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 小春一旦決定了就很頑固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我再想想另外還有沒有什麼方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之前決定不要連接「全球網路」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(821,655)}<Global Net>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉了啊 一直說著任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春也還收著那些拖鞋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家的在小學六年級的時候被父母扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小千
Comment: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的打算全部吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用一次吃掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次吃掉天使屋的冰淇淋就是我的夢想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也說了只要請吃這個就原諒你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不吃完的話就不能原諒你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想快點把事情結束掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次在學校見面 小春就一副很抱歉的樣子看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓也是 一見面就道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為小千 感覺一直在生氣的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想生氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說「可以了 我完全不在意」的話也很奇怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那確實是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些啊 你們兩個打算繼續玩那個Brain什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為黑雪學姐很熱衷 所以你們也很熱衷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學姐確實是一個契機 但不僅僅是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我做出了那種事 「Brain Burst」本身沒有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是 小春「虛擬角色」的是完全飛行型…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(584,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不懂 總之不就是個格鬥遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起說明 實際看一下可能會比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千 把那邊的辭典扔向我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？向阿拓扔？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能明白「Brain Burst」的力量 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 說得好像只有你們明白似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 我會認真扔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得是偶然的話 可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(639,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算是小千也明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「Brain Burst」的真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得火氣都上來了 而且肚子也餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是懲罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拓 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點啊 會化掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就吃特別布丁吧 阿拓吃哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 松糕 草莓草莓櫻桃 危險香蕉 巧克力板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,板…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是巧克力薄荷之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小春還只是等級2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouncer啊 還有Bouncer這個方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.40,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,註：Bouncer 美國口語中的保鑣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouncer？
Comment: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很…很適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個只是因為吃東西的時候會礙事 隨便束了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比起那個 出院時間已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要跟這個牢飯說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 組隊對戰的戰果如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在出院前能升到等級2嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如…如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經升級了 要是她說讓我看看的話就很麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 想在出院的同時將空白的杉並區
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣佈為「黑暗星雲」的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\pos(641,655)}<Nega Nebulas>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是應該等你升到等級2呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是 今天之後也會稍微對戰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這之後？和拓武一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雖然這麼說 也不要心急
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上升級到等級2的話 剩餘的點數就很危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我想你應該也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 學姐 罵我是個笨蛋吧
Comment: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道會不會被看見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 有什麼事的話馬上聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouncer是「Brain Burst」內存在的 唯一的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保鏢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也在觀戰時見過好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「虛擬角色」的名字是「Aqua Current」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(408,655)}<Avatar>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線者」的點數跌到危險區域時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(440,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到恢復到安全區域為止 會一直作為你組隊對戰的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事也能做到嗎 很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他的外號是「The One」也就是等級1
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等級1做保鏢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能做到 實際上也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上雇傭的話也有各種條件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 作為雇傭他的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最高到等級2為止的「超頻連線者」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(835,655)}<Burst Linker>
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 雇主必須表露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實暴露的風險就是報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 聽說是我的現實不行 一定要是本人的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的 那麼要如何表露
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要到指定的碰面地點才能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是一個人去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能什麼事都要求安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷跟著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴露的話可能不會再來見第二次面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個包包是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 不是你要約的人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.73,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,231)\frz341.556}輸入姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:03.48,Comment,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(440,45,452,250,150,380)\frz11.533}報酬確實收到了\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N　　　　　　　　13點40分開始開始進行委託的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz10.52\pos(602,386)}整理準備 就此待機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13點40分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是到40分就「超頻連線」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(742,655)}<Burst Link>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說 她在哪裡看著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在想也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 去一下洗手間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一到書店就那麼想去洗手間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:19:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是「Aqua Current」？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個包包並不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請還給我
Comment: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好睏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 黛在之前的大賽上贏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他不出場的話明明是有機會的 我們的男子隊也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黛…阿拓？
Comment: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 是不是裝作沒注意到比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒想到是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是保鏢 還以為肯定是男的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是她不接受我的委託的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說要在這裡直連？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人好大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…男女直連 一般都是更親密之後再進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方直連的話會招到誤解…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓別人聽到對話內容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種強硬 不容說不的感覺 跟學姊好像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Comment: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「超頻連線」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.36,0:22:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(641,655)}<Burst Link>
Comment: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.42,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}We are tossed by the waves of pain and tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.25,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}I'm tossed into the fray tossed by various fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.88,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}Flashed in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.38,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}It's a 「Burst」 of sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:31.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「諦め」がくれた 安楽 沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.66,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.75,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.10,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わらずにいてと願うこと-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.76,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}-変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:47.93,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}本当の声を…言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.22,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.20,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.49,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.81,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「今度こそは…」 つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:06.07,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.37,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.59,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.92,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}歪む世界 走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.16,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.76,ED-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「真実」と 加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:15.42,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們遭受淚水與傷痛煩心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.42,0:22:19.25,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}而我被置身於那亂於無數未來的競爭之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將自身覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.88,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}閃現於高空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.38,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}這就是「加速」快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:31.66,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}「放棄」帶來的安樂停滯世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.66,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}何時悄然而至的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:37.75,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}恍然間光輝耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.10,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}祈求永恆無變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.76,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}我們卻生活在幻化無常的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:47.93,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}搭載著吐露的真聲與難以言說的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.22,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與你一同展翅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.20,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}讓聲音迴蕩在天際！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:56.16,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加的堅強…用雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.49,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}將淚水全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.81,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}喃喃而道「下次一定…」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:06.07,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}不會讓傷痛僅僅成為過往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:09.37,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}更加快速地…到達你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:12.59,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}即使羽翼已支離破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.67,0:23:15.92,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}仍會奔跑在這個扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:19.16,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}依循著感覺的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:24.76,ED-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\be1\fad(100,100)}與「真實」一同加速
